            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " TWO CYLINDRICAL BENZENE LIQUID SCINTILLATORS",
                "        EACH CONTAINING 1 LITRE NE 230, LOCATED AT",
                "        90 DEGREES TO THE BEAM AXIS AT A DISTANCE OF",
                "        4 CM FROM THE SAMPLE."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SHAPE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " RESONANCE PARAMETERS WERE EXTRACTED FROM THE CAPTURE",
                " YIELDS USING THE CODE 'FANAC' DESCRIBED IN",
                " F.H.FROEHNER, KFK-2145, KERNFORSCHUNGSZENTRUM",
                " KARLSRUHE (1977)",
                ".ALL THE KNOWN RESONANCES OF ALL THE IRON ISOTOPES,",
                " TOGETHER WITH THOSE FOR OXYGEN IN THE CASE OF FE-58,",
                " WERE INCLUDED IN THE FIT."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": null,
                "reaction": {
                  "code": "79-AU-197(N,G)79-AU-198,,SIG",
                  "code_unit": [
                    {
                      "unit": "79-AU-197(N,G)79-AU-198,,SIG",
                      "field": {
                        "reaction": "79-AU-197(N,G)79-AU-198",
                        "target": "79-AU-197",
                        "projectile": "N",
                        "process": "G",
                        "product": "79-AU-198",
                        "quantity": ",SIG",
                        "data_type": null,
                        "general_quantity_modifier": null,
                        "quantity_236": ",SIG"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " THE NORMALISATION WAS PERFORMED IN THREE WAYS -",
                "  1) THE EXPERIMENTAL TOF SPECTRUM OF THE GOLD",
                "     SAMPLE WAS SMOOTHED STRONGLY, AND THE SMOOTH",
                "     CROSS SECTION FROM ENDF/B-IV WAS TAKEN AS A",
                "     REFERENCE.",
                "  2) THE EXPERIMENTAL TOF SPECTRUM OF THE GOLD",
                "     SAMPLE WAS SMOOTHED SLIGHTLY AND THE CROSS",
                "     SECTION WAS TAKEN FROM ENDF/B-V, AVERAGED",
                "     OVER 1 KEV INTERVALS.",
                "  3) THE TOF SPECTRUM OF THE GOLD SAMPLE WAS USED",
                "     WITHOUT SMOOTHING AND THE CROSS SECTION FROM",
                "     FROM ENDF/B-V WAS TAKEN WITH FULL RESOLUTION."
              ]
            }
          ],
